name: Faceted amethyst and black onyx set
description:
This faceted amethyst and black onyx set is sparkly beyond belief!

This set uses semi-precious gemstones and contains the following:

(1) Necklace 
(2) Stretch bracelet 
(3) Earrings - choose from:
(3.a) sterling silver shepherd hook with dangle;
(3.b) silver plated continental closed wire, long and narrow amethyst;
(3.c) silver plated continental closed wire, short and wide amethyst.

The earrings are faceted amethyst only.
The stretch bracelet contains a  mix of faceted amethyst shapes and faceted black onyx.
The matching necklace also contains a  mix of faceted amethyst shapes and faceted black onyx.

This set comes from the Princess Spring 2012 collection.

Designed and crafted by Alice Letts for Alice Stories Handmade Jewellery.

name: Black onyx and red bubble set
description:
Black onyx and red bubble set on sterling silver contains the following:

(1) Necklace; and
(2) Earrings 

The necklace is set on a silver coloured beading wire finished with a silver plated lobster clasp.  The beads are semi-precious gemstones including faceted black onyx, small red chinese jade, faceted carnelian, and black tourmaline.

The earrings are made using sterling silver and dangle from sterling silver shepherd hooks.

This set comes from the Princess 2012 collection.

Designed and crafted by Alice Letts for Alice Stories Handmade Jewellery.

Copyright 2012, Alice Stories Handmade Jewellery, all rights reserved.

name: Smoky quartz and gold plated sterling silver set
description:
The genuine smoky quartz set contains the following

(1) Choose from one of two pairs of earrings:
(1.a)  Smoky quartz drop on a long narrow gold plated sterling silver connector hanging from a gold plated sterling silver dome and stud earrings with gold plated sterling silver findings; or

(1.b)  Smoky quartz drop on a wide gold plated sterling silver connector hanging from a gold plated continental style clasp earrings with gold plated sterling silver findings; 

(2) Necklace with three smoky quartz drops dangling on a gold coloured beading wire and gold plated lobster clasp.

This set comes from the Princess Spring 2012 collection.

description:

(2) Bracelet with large paua shell with a gold plated sterling silver clasp;
(3)  Necklace with oval paua shell drops and genuine dark pearls and sardonyx tubes with a gold plated sterling silver clasp.
